   Analyze the dependence of the inflationary observables on the number of species $N_s$. Determine if $N_s$ is a free parameter or if the dynamical selection mechanism forces $N_s$ toward a specific value to maintain the metastable state. Provide a physical argument for the range $N_s \sim 10^8$ by relating it to the saturation of the information storage capacity of the de Sitter horizon at the inflationary scale.

